abstract: North Korea lashed back at the United States for taking issue with its human rights record on Saturday, saying Washington's "malicious words" would only aggravate tensions on the Korean Peninsula, state news agency KCNA reported.
snippet: North Korea lashed back at the United States for taking issue with its human rights record on Saturday, saying Washington's "malicious words" would only aggravate tensions on the Korean Peninsula, state news agency KCNA reported.
lead_paragraph: SEOUL — North Korea lashed back at the United States for taking issue with its human rights record on Saturday, saying Washington's "malicious words" would only aggravate tensions on the Korean Peninsula, state news agency KCNA reported.
headline_main: North Korea Warns U.S. Could 'Pay Dearly' for Human Rights Criticism
headline_print_headline: North Korea Warns U.S. Could 'Pay Dearly' for Human Rights Criticism

abstract: Steven Whitley scored 16 points, Kashaun Hicks added 13 and Norfolk State beat Bowling Green 72-67 in overtime on Friday night at the Battle of the Boardwalk to end an eight-game skid.
snippet: Steven Whitley scored 16 points, Kashaun Hicks added 13 and Norfolk State beat Bowling Green 72-67 in overtime on Friday night at the Battle of the Boardwalk to end an eight-game skid.
lead_paragraph: ATLANTIC CITY, N.J. — Steven Whitley scored 16 points, Kashaun Hicks added 13 and Norfolk State beat Bowling Green 72-67 in overtime on Friday night at the Battle of the Boardwalk to end an eight-game skid.
headline_main: Norfolk State Tops Bowling Green 72-67 in OT
headline_print_headline: Norfolk State Tops Bowling Green 72-67 in OT

abstract: Justin Champagnie had 14 points and 10 rebounds to lead Pittsburgh to a 79-53 rout of Binghamton on Friday.
snippet: Justin Champagnie had 14 points and 10 rebounds to lead Pittsburgh to a 79-53 rout of Binghamton on Friday.
lead_paragraph: PITTSBURGH — Justin Champagnie had 14 points and 10 rebounds to lead Pittsburgh to a 79-53 rout of Binghamton on Friday.
headline_main: Champagnie Leads Pitt to Rout of Binghamton
headline_print_headline: Champagnie Leads Pitt to Rout of Binghamton

abstract: The financial transaction tax on share dealing that 10 European countries hope to introduce from 2021 could be extended to cover trading in riskier assets, German finance minister Olaf Scholz said.
snippet: The financial transaction tax on share dealing that 10 European countries hope to introduce from 2021 could be extended to cover trading in riskier assets, German finance minister Olaf Scholz said.
lead_paragraph: BERLIN — The financial transaction tax on share dealing that 10 European countries hope to introduce from 2021 could be extended to cover trading in riskier assets, German finance minister Olaf Scholz said.
headline_main: German Finmin-Tax on Share Dealing Could Be Extended to Other Assets
headline_print_headline: German Finmin-Tax on Share Dealing Could Be Extended to Other Assets

abstract: Maurice Howard had a season-high 24 points as Alcorn State rolled past NCCAA-member Ecclesia 122-71 on Friday in its final nonconference game of the season.
snippet: Maurice Howard had a season-high 24 points as Alcorn State rolled past NCCAA-member Ecclesia 122-71 on Friday in its final nonconference game of the season.
lead_paragraph: LORMAN, Miss. — Maurice Howard had a season-high 24 points as Alcorn State rolled past NCCAA-member Ecclesia 122-71 on Friday in its final nonconference game of the season.
headline_main: Howard Scores 24 to Lead Alcorn St. Over Ecclesia 122-71
headline_print_headline: Howard Scores 24 to Lead Alcorn St. Over Ecclesia 122-71

abstract: Almark Foods said the voluntary recall affected hard-boiled and peeled eggs that were sold in white plastic pails to restaurants and grocery stores for use in egg salad and other foods.
snippet: Almark Foods said the voluntary recall affected hard-boiled and peeled eggs that were sold in white plastic pails to restaurants and grocery stores for use in egg salad and other foods.
lead_paragraph: A Georgia food company said Friday that it was recalling hard-boiled eggs that were sold in bulk and linked to a listeria outbreak that led to sicknesses in five states, including one death and four hospitalizations.

abstract: A man convicted of kidnapping a Wisconsin girl and killing her parents told police after his arrest that he never thought Jayme Closs would escape because she was petrified, and that after holding her captive for two weeks, he believed he'd get away with his crimes, according to a transcript of a police interview.
snippet: A man convicted of kidnapping a Wisconsin girl and killing her parents told police after his arrest that he never thought Jayme Closs would escape because she was petrified, and that after holding her captive for two weeks, he believed he'd get aw...
lead_paragraph: MINNEAPOLIS — A man convicted of kidnapping a Wisconsin girl and killing her parents told police after his arrest that he never thought Jayme Closs would escape because she was petrified, and that after holding her captive for two weeks, he believed he'd get away with his crimes, according to a transcript of a police interview.
headline_main: Man Who Kidnapped Wisconsin Teen: She Was 'Terrified of Me'
